  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A minor turbulence-model coefficient update was applied on 2025-11-10 to improve near-wall shear resolution; the primary experimental hemolysis dataset was collected and frozen on 2025-10-17, approximately three weeks prior to that revision. The assessment team judged the coefficient change not material to the dataset's relevance and proceeded without formal re-validation against the updated model build.",
