      "description": "Time-averaged velocity and pressure profiles at pump inlet and outlet planes, derived from Doppler ultrasound measurements conducted in Q3 2025. These boundary conditions are used as CFD inlet BCs for all five operating points. Vintage predates the model revision but the assessment team considered the BC profiles geometry-driven and therefore insensitive to the turbulence coefficient change.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-09-05T00:00:00Z",
      "format": "HDF5",
      "source": "Morrison Lab experimental campaign, batch BC-2025-Q3"
