      "rationale": "k-omega SST selected based on internal benchmarks for pump flows; however, the November coefficient update was not re-benchmarked. The Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law model is used despite known limitations for low-shear exposure paths in centrifugal pumps. Model form uncertainty not formally propagated to NIH."
